data.name: laySayu.QuerySQL
data.value: SELECT A.LAB_NO, A.SPECIMEN_CODE, A.EMERGENCY, ' ' PASSWARD, A.GUMSAJA, ' ' DUMMY, A.REF_COMMENT, A.HANGMOG_CODE, A.BEFORE_GUMSAJA, A.BEFORE_RESULT, A.CANCEL_DATE, A.CANCEL_TIME, ' ' FROM CPL3088 A WHERE A.HOSP_CODE = :f_hosp_code AND A.LAB_NO = :f_lab_no AND A.HANGMOG_CODE = :f_hangmog_code AND A.SPECIMEN_CODE = :f_specimen_code AND A.EMERGENCY = :f_emergency ORDER BY RPAD(A.CANCEL_DATE,12,'0')||RPAD(A.CANCEL_TIME,4,'0')
